Initial file is supercell.gro which is created from experimental structure. This file is used to prepare the crystal seed.



1.  Energy minimization: Steepest descent minimization was performed until the maximum force on each atom was ≤ 50 kJ/mol/nm.

2.  NVT equilibration: The system was equilibrated for 750 ps using a 2 fs time step at a target temperature of 298 K.

3.  NPT equilibration: Anisotropic Parrinello–Rahman pressure coupling at 1 bar was applied through three consecutive runs of 100 ns (0.1 fs), 3.5 ns (0.2 fs), and 2.5 ns (0.4 fs) time steps.

4.  NPT production: A 25 ns production run was performed under NPT conditions at 1 bar using the Parrinello–Rahman barostat with a 0.2 fs time step
